  // ── Mobile swipe-to-advance ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
  // Chrome commits scroll direction at touchstart, before the first touchmove.
  // So calling e.preventDefault() in touchmove is too late on Chrome — the
  // browser has already taken ownership of the gesture.
